ральной (автор даже приводит случаи из театральной жизни ХХ века, когда актерам <a href="/review/846369">дальше…</a></p> </td> \n                 </tr> \n                 <tr> \n                  <td class="author-story-bottom"> <a href="/reader/Rediso4ka"><span class="user-pic" style="background-image: url(https://j.livelib.ru/userpic/Rediso4ka/30x30/7340/Rediso4ka.jpg);"></span>Rediso4ka</a> </td> \n                  <td style="width:20px;"></td> \n                  <td class="author-story-bottom"> <a href="/reader/Grandmama"><span class="user-pic" style="background-image: url(https://i.livelib.ru/userpic/Grandmama/30x30/9476/Grandmama.jpg);"></span>Grandmama</a> </td> \n                 </tr> \n                </tbody>\n               </table> </li> \n             </ul> \n            </div> \n            <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="prev-carousel"></a> \n            <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="next-carousel"></a> \n           </div> \n          </div> \n          <div class="separator">\n           <!-- -->\n          </div> \n          <h2 class="game-title event-pad" style="margin-bottom:5px;">Смотрите также:</h2> •&nbsp;\n          <a style="font-weight: bold;" class="list-nav" href="/authors/prosaists">Авторы-прозаики</a> \n         </div> \n         <div class="separator"></div> \n        </div> \n        <div class="column-240 subcontainer"> \n         <div id="column-absolute" class="column-absolute"> \n          <div id="column-fixed" class="column-fixed"> \n           <div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;display:block !important;"> \n            <div class="meganfox pad side-blocks">\n             <!-- Litres - RU - PB - 240x400 - ATF --> \n             <script type="text/javascript" data-pagespeed-no-defer>pagespeed.lazyLoadImages.overrideAttributeFunctions();</script>\n             <script type="text/javascript">\r\n<!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   document.MAX_ct0 =''INSERT_CLICK_URL'';\r\n   var m3_u = (location